                <p>Restrictions & Timeline: Holiday Weekends. Based upon availability and prevailing length of stay restrictions. (Kindly note: Holiday weekends may include local festivals & local school holiday weekends.  Please be sure to inquire directly with the property. Blackout dates apply.)</p>
                <p>Conditions: Non-Transferrable. No Cash Value. Up to $75 Halyard Restaurant credit processed as in-house food & beverage hotel charge.</p>
                <p>Total Fair Market Value for Sound View Greenport:  $900</p>
                <p>Total Fair Market Value for Lo &amp; Sons:  $236-696</p>

            </div>
        </div>
        <button class="panel-close"><span class="sr-only">close</span></button>
    </div>
   

</article>